Subject: drm/amdkfd: print address in hex format rather than decimal
Git-commit: ae0448bc88b7827babda73edfe587ccc222baccc
Patch-mainline: v6.0-rc5
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225 jsc#PED-2849

Addresses should be printed in hex format.

Signed-off-by: Yifan Zhang <yifan1.zhang@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Felix Kuehling <Felix.Kuehling@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Acked-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_amdkfd_gpuvm.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_amdkfd_gpuvm.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_amdkfd_gpuvm.c
index cbd593f7d553..2170db83e41d 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_amdkfd_gpuvm.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/amdgpu_amdkfd_gpuvm.c
@@ -1728,7 +1728,7 @@ int amdgpu_amdkfd_gpuvm_alloc_memory_of_gpu(
 	add_kgd_mem_to_kfd_bo_list(*mem, avm->process_info, user_addr);
 
 	if (user_addr) {
-		pr_debug("creating userptr BO for user_addr = %llu\n", user_addr);
+		pr_debug("creating userptr BO for user_addr = %llx\n", user_addr);
 		ret = init_user_pages(*mem, user_addr, criu_resume);
 		if (ret)
 			goto allocate_init_user_pages_failed;
